  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Provide hygiene education to village in India</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will educate 250 children and caregivers in India, together, on life-saving hygiene practices such as hand washing, bathing, tooth brushing, and clean water collection &amp; storage in efforts to facilitate co-learning and reinforcement of behavior change at home. Rights and responsibilities are central themes - emphasizing the importance of empowering children from a young age to take responsibility for their health and well-being.</narrative>
  </description>
